JSON Data type validation was added in
https://github.com/CESNET/libyang/commit/10bafbb9a787d65a5a4d600dd76982024fc3ffa4

Unfortunately since SONiC is well established and there are lots of users that aren't
strictly conforming with JSON data types, we cannot enable this.  There are lots of
test cases that will fail as well due to the use of the wrong data type.

Revert

